EmailTemplate.name: Go Mobile
EmailTemplate.subject: Smart Phone Mobile CRM
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.FirstName},
Stay in the game no matter where you are. VinSolutions mobile CRM keeps you up to the minute whether you’re on the lot or on the course.
Your sales team will be able to virtually instantly view and respond to leads, sold counts, appointments, view inventory, send emails and much more.
Managers will know what is going on at anytime across the entire organization without being chained down to a computer screen – all this from the phone already in your pocket! Brendan M. Shea {!User.Username} 619.507.8454
